      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Gnomes gain the following spell-like abilities (see CRB page 262): 1/day—@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.rSWg5JnN3mxzkatD]{Dancing Lights}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.J1k3B5PmIc4SUC9L]{Ghost Sound}, and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.kNURbWD9d5768exU]{Token Spell}. The caster level for these effects is equal to the gnome’s character level. In addition, gnomes get a +2 racial saving throw bonus against illusion spells and effects.</p>"
